CatDescriptText: Pomeroyal C. Fountain, swimming instructor, lived at 3107 Centre Avenue in 1938-41.  In 1945 Fountain is listed as "physical director" at the Centre Avenue YMCA and in 1948 as a teacher at the A. Leo Weil Elementary School.  He died before 1951.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys swim team and coach Pomeroyal Fountain, posed at edge of swimming pool, possibly in Soho Bath House
